ButterNotes v1.1 - "Project Perfection"
🧈 The definitive suckless note-taking experience

Features:
- Lightning-fast fzf file browser with grouped display
- Project organization through subdirectories  
- Content search with exact line navigation
- Seamless workflow: browse → search → edit → repeat
- Clean exits, no friction, pure keyboard-driven
- Template system for quick note creation
- File moving between projects
- Integrates perfectly with nvim markdown rendering

Workflow:
- notes: Browse all notes (grouped by project)
- Ctrl-S: Search content → select → jumps to exact line
- Ctrl-N: Create new note
- Ctrl-M: Move note between projects
- ESC: Clean exit at any point

Essential keybinds only:
- Enter: Open
- Ctrl-N: New  
- Ctrl-D: Delete
- Ctrl-S: Search
- Ctrl-M: Move

Zero redundancy. Maximum efficiency. Pure suckless.

